definition.value: An  ecdysteroid that is ecdysone substituted by a hydroxy group at position 20.
The S-phenyl derivative of N-acetyl-L-cysteine. It is a urinary metabolite of benzene and used as a biomarker to assess benzene exposure.
Galactaric acid in which the hydrogen of one of the alcoholic hydroxy groups has been replaced by a feruloyl group.
